msgctxt "392_Kiryu"
msgid "Ever heard of 777 Town?"
msgstr "¿Alguna vez has oído hablar de 777 Town?"

msgctxt "404_Maya"
msgid "777 Town? What's that?"
msgstr "¿777 Town? ¿Y eso qué es?"

msgctxt "416_Kiryu"
msgid "It's a game for your computer or cell phone. It lets you play pachinko and slots anytime you want."
msgstr "It's a game for your computer or cell phone. It lets you play pachinko and slots anytime you want."

msgctxt "428_Maya"
msgid "Sounds fun! I've always wanted to try pachinko."
msgstr "¡Se ve divertido! ¡Siempre quise probar el pachinko."

msgctxt "440_Kiryu"
msgid "Good. It'd be a nice warm-up for the real thing."
msgstr "Bien. Sería un buen calentamiento para lo que viene."

msgctxt "452_Maya"
msgid "Yeah! I'll check it out."
msgstr "¡Claro! Lo probaré."

msgctxt "464_Kiryu"
msgid "Ever heard of Amoebatar?"
msgstr "¿Has oído hablar de Amoebatar?"

msgctxt "476_Maya"
msgid "Of course! I'm on it all the time."
msgstr "Of course! I'm on it all the time."

msgctxt "488_Kiryu"
msgid "So your avatar looks just like you, right?"
msgstr "So your avatar looks just like you, right?"

msgctxt "500_Maya"
msgid "Yep! Try and find me, okay? Let's play a game together next time you're on. <Color:7>♥<Color:Default>"
msgstr "Yep! Try and find me, okay? Let's play a game together next time you're on. <Color:7>♥<Color:Default>"

msgctxt "512_Kiryu"
msgid "Sounds good."
msgstr "Me parece bien."

msgctxt "524_Kiryu"
msgid "Hear about the ghost in the underground mall?"
msgstr "¿Escuchaste sobre el fantasma que hay en el centro comercial subterráneo?"

msgctxt "536_Maya"
msgid "Oh, c'mon. I'm not that gullible!"
msgstr "Oh, c'mon. I'm not that gullible!"

msgctxt "548_Kiryu"
msgid "I'm not pulling your leg. Apparently, when they were first building the mall, a construction worker died in an accident."
msgstr "I'm not pulling your leg. Apparently, when they were first building the mall, a construction worker died in an accident."

msgctxt "560_Kiryu"
msgid "Now, night after night, his ghost appears to wander the empty mall."
msgstr "Ahora, cuando cae la noche, su fantasma deambula por el centro comercial vacío."

msgctxt "572_Maya"
msgid "Sounds like something a drunk thought he saw."
msgstr "Sounds like something a drunk thought he saw."

msgctxt "584_Kiryu"
msgid "Oh... I find that strangely convincing..."
msgstr "Oh... I find that strangely convincing..."

msgctxt "596_Kiryu"
msgid "Hear about the footbaths at Yunosono Hot Springs? You don't take off your clothes, so men and women can go in together."
msgstr "¿Has oído hablar de los baños de pies de las Aguas termales Yunosono? No hace falta que te quites la ropa, así que hombres y mujeres pueden entrar juntos."

msgctxt "608_Maya"
msgid "Oh really? I'd love to go."
msgstr "Oh really? I'd love to go."

msgctxt "620_Kiryu"
msgid "Do you go to the hot springs a lot?"
msgstr "Do you go to the hot springs a lot?"

msgctxt "632_Maya"
msgid "Yes, I do. One time, I got this intense urge to go and took a trip to Nikko that same day."
msgstr "Yes, I do. One time, I got this intense urge to go and took a trip to Nikko that same day."

msgctxt "644_Kiryu"
msgid "That's impressive."
msgstr "That's impressive."

msgctxt "656_Kiryu"
msgid "Golf is starting to get pretty popular. A lot of couples go on golf dates nowadays."
msgstr "El golf se está volviendo muy popular últimamente. Hoy en día muchas parejas tienen citas en el golf."

msgctxt "668_Maya"
msgid "Golf dates? Sounds pretty fancy."
msgstr "Golf dates? Sounds pretty fancy."

msgctxt "680_Kiryu"
msgid "You're too busy with work to exercise, right? A refreshing round of golf might do you some good."
msgstr "You're too busy with work to exercise, right? A refreshing round of golf might do you some good."

msgctxt "692_Maya"
msgid "Hehe, maybe! Let's go together sometime!"
msgstr "Hehe, maybe! Let's go together sometime!"

msgctxt "704_Kiryu"
msgid "Do you eat liver? Liver contains arachidonic acid, which reverses aging in the brain."
msgstr "¿Has comido higado? El hígado contiene ácido araquidónico, que revierte el envejecimiento del cerebro."

msgctxt "716_Maya"
msgid "I love liver sashimi. I especially like to change up the flavor when I eat it. Garlic soy sauce, sesame sauce, it's all so good."
msgstr "I love liver sashimi. I especially like to change up the flavor when I eat it. Garlic soy sauce, sesame sauce, it's all so good."

msgctxt "728_Kiryu"
msgid "Then you've probably got a good memory, thanks to the liver."
msgstr "Then you've probably got a good memory, thanks to the liver."

msgctxt "740_Maya"
msgid "Um, I don't think so. When I drink, I end up forgetting things."
msgstr "Um, I don't think so. When I drink, I end up forgetting things."

msgctxt "752_Kiryu"
msgid "Oh."
msgstr "Oh."

msgctxt "764_Kiryu"
msgid "Did you know pole dancing is great for working out?"
msgstr "¿Sabías que el pole dance es genial para hacer ejercicio?"

msgctxt "776_Maya"
msgid "I do know. One of my friends is doing it."
msgstr "I do know. One of my friends is doing it."

msgctxt "788_Kiryu"
msgid "Is she? So she's got a slim figure, right?"
msgstr "Is she? So she's got a slim figure, right?"

msgctxt "800_Maya"
msgid "Oh, not just slim. Pole dancing gets you pretty buff. Her arms and thighs are really muscular."
msgstr "Oh, not just slim. Pole dancing gets you pretty buff. Her arms and thighs are really muscular."

msgctxt "812_Kiryu"
msgid "That so?"
msgstr "Ya veo."

msgctxt "824_Kiryu"
msgid "Sweet sake is all the rage now. Women like to order it when eating over at Sushi Gin."
msgstr "Sweet sake is all the rage now. Women like to order it when eating over at Sushi Gin."

msgctxt "836_Maya"
msgid "Oh, I love sweet sake! It's so delicious and easy to drink."
msgstr "Oh, I love sweet sake! It's so delicious and easy to drink."

msgctxt "848_Kiryu"
msgid "And it's got a low alcohol percentage, so even you won't drink yourself under the table."
msgstr "And it's got a low alcohol percentage, so even you won't drink yourself under the table."

msgctxt "860_Maya"
msgid "True. It's the perfect drink for a girls night out."
msgstr "True. It's the perfect drink for a girls night out."

msgctxt "908_Kiryu"
msgid "Did you try out 777 Town yet?"
msgstr "¿Aún no has probado 777 Town?"

msgctxt "920_Maya"
msgid "I did! It's really addictive."
msgstr "I did! It's really addictive."

msgctxt "932_Maya"
msgid "In fact, I'm a little sleep deprived because of it."
msgstr "In fact, I'm a little sleep deprived because of it."

msgctxt "944_Kiryu"
msgid "Heh. That so?"
msgstr "Je, je, ¿en serio?"

msgctxt "956_Kiryu"
msgid "So about Amoebatar... You're on it, right?"
msgstr "So about Amoebatar... You're on it, right?"

msgctxt "968_Maya"
msgid "That's right! Did you find my avatar? It looks exactly like me."
msgstr "That's right! Did you find my avatar? It looks exactly like me."

msgctxt "980_Kiryu"
msgid "Um, I haven't quite gotten around to it yet..."
msgstr "Um, I haven't quite gotten around to it yet..."

msgctxt "992_Kiryu"
msgid "So about that ghost in the underground mall..."
msgstr "Acerca del fantasma del centro comercial..."

msgctxt "1004_Maya"
msgid "That again? Come on, someone only thought they saw it. It doesn't exist!"
msgstr "That again? Come on, someone only thought they saw it. It doesn't exist!"

msgctxt "1016_Kiryu"
msgid "Yeah, I guess there's no proof..."
msgstr "Yeah, I guess there's no proof..."

msgctxt "1028_Maya"
msgid "That's right. If it was real, it would've been caught on a security camera or something."
msgstr "That's right. If it was real, it would've been caught on a security camera or something."

msgctxt "1040_Kiryu"
msgid "......"
msgstr "......"

msgctxt "1052_Kiryu"
msgid "Try out the footbaths at Yunosono Hot Springs yet?"
msgstr "¿Ya probaste los baños de pies en las aguas termales Yunosono?"

msgctxt "1064_Maya"
msgid "I did! I never knew there were footbaths so close by."
msgstr "I did! I never knew there were footbaths so close by."

msgctxt "1076_Kiryu"
msgid "And you don't have to worry about staying in for too long. You can just relax."
msgstr "And you don't have to worry about staying in for too long. You can just relax."

msgctxt "1088_Kiryu"
msgid "Played any golf recently?"
msgstr "Played any golf recently?"

msgctxt "1100_Maya"
msgid "Work's been keeping me busy. I just don't have enough time."
msgstr "Work's been keeping me busy. I just don't have enough time."

msgctxt "1112_Kiryu"
msgid "Ah. Must be tough."
msgstr "Ah. Debe ser duro."

msgctxt "1124_Kiryu"
msgid "Did you know that liver contains arachidonic acid, which reverses aging in the brain?"
msgstr "Did you know that liver contains arachidonic acid, which reverses aging in the brain?"

msgctxt "1136_Maya"
msgid "I think you've told me this before."
msgstr "I think you've told me this before."

msgctxt "1148_Kiryu"
msgid "Oh, really? Hmm..."
msgstr "Oh, really? Hmm..."

msgctxt "1160_Maya"
msgid "Maybe you're the one who needs to start eating liver."
msgstr "Maybe you're the one who needs to start eating liver."

msgctxt "1172_Kiryu"
msgid "......"
msgstr "......"

msgctxt "1184_Kiryu"
msgid "About that pole dancing workout..."
msgstr "Sobre hacer ejercicio con pole dance..."

msgctxt "1196_Kiryu"
msgid "It doesn't look like you need it at all."
msgstr "It doesn't look like you need it at all."

msgctxt "1208_Maya"
msgid "Hehe. I'm a model! I'm pretty confident in my figure."
msgstr "Hehe. I'm a model! I'm pretty confident in my figure."

msgctxt "1220_Kiryu"
msgid "Have you been drinking sweet sake lately?"
msgstr "Have you been drinking sweet sake lately?"

msgctxt "1232_Maya"
msgid "Not lately. I'm not always tipping the bottle back, you know?"
msgstr "Not lately. I'm not always tipping the bottle back, you know?"

msgctxt "1244_Maya"
msgid "What kind of person do you think I am?"
msgstr "What kind of person do you think I am?"

msgctxt "1256_Kiryu"
msgid "Sorry..."
msgstr "Lo siento..."

